name: Property Data
query:
SELECT lc.name AS 'Lease Contract Name',
       lc.lease_customer AS 'Lease Customer',
       lc.property_name AS 'Property Name',
       lc.unit_name AS 'Unit Name',
       lc.rent_start_date AS 'Rent Start Date',
       lc.rent_end_date AS 'Rent End Date'
FROM `tabLease Contract` lc
LEFT JOIN `tabLease Item` li ON li.parent = lc.name
ORDER BY lc.rent_start_date ASC
